title: Naturally-Lit 1BR Apartment Home at the Historic Grand Apartments
posting_body: ['Property Address', '1962 Grand Ave - 301(R)', '| St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 08/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Available 8/1: Spacious, front-corner apartment home in the heart of Grand Ave!', 'This spacious one-bedroom apartment home sits in the front corner of the building, meaning your home will always be illuminated with natural sunlight!', "You'll also have access to a fully remodeled kitchen, including new cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and hardwood flooring.", 'The kitchen has an open layout that leads into a dining area overlooking Grand Ave.', 'You will enjoy the treetop view through the large, updated windows!', 'Situated between the University of St. Thomas and Macalester College, the Historic Grand Apartments are in an ideal location.', 'Spacious layouts, historic charm, restored hardwood floors, and beautiful built-ins make historic living unbeatable.', "There are many local shops and restaurants within walking distance, and you'll be able to catch the bus for convenient commuting downtown.", 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Controlled Entry', 'Laundry On-Site', 'On Bus Route', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 750', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,127.00', 'Available: 08/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
